{"tid":1493992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咩五大訴求？】獨立調查委員會有撚用呀","createTime":"2019-08-21T13:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T15:54:10.000Z","uid":189593,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24744888b2e05f7280e54d2944a32e1902fd46ea","tid":1493992,"uid":189593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思口氣重左引大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於政府突然鬆口話做獨立調查委員會，我唔知大家點諗，但相信大家都心照，一定唔會信個垃圾委員會會公平公正公開咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我陰謀論，點解突然咁多警方黑料爆出，變相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />低頭認有部分警員做錯，好似想割某些警員，再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做PR咁以保警隊形象<br />\n<br />\n唔想政府有藉口逃避，到時只會俾人覺得政府/警隊做錯但都補救左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuBhFmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuBhFmf.jpg&h=b74c7333&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wk5a0mi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWk5a0mi.jpg&h=e9e9e7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqKbKN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqKbKN2.jpg&h=0f92e9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇政策/法律巴可以草案出監警法 + 警制改革 + 獨立調查委員會規定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20fc347d4a1e10b9e0d0dc4576786f934d02a11","tid":1493992,"uid":40697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思,借一借位<br />\n<br />\n[係咪咁撚鍾意俾人監控?]824!觀塘要人 824!觀塘需要你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e3707b09b77af2b702b9af032c85f3d1370